Title: News From Beneath
Description:
Before I arrived, I was informed that the Life-Binder has need of our aid. There is news of the Incarnates, and she requests our presence at the Seat of the Aspects.

As for Emberthal -- there is very little we can do for now. It is best we allow her to reflect and gather thoughts alone.
ObjectivesText: Meet Alexstrasza at the Seat of the Aspects in Valdrakken.

Objectives.Text: Travel to the Seat of the Aspects
